  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Rey Jesús jamonqa kay pachaman
 Mayjatun atiyninwanña./
 /Tlikuy wawasnin jaqay cielopi
 Kusikamusun wiñaypajmin./
 
[V2]
 /Kusikuy kanqa jaqay p'unchaypi
 Diospa uyanta rikuspa./
 Manchay Iliphipej k'anchaj llajtampi
 Kusikuyilapi chaypi kasun./
 
[V3]
 /Qanrí hermano, listochu kanki
 Salvadorwan rinaykipaj?/
 /Sichus Señorta qan qhesachawaj,
 Mana kanqachu kusiyniyki./
 
</lyrics></song>